::DarkMouse::

"AHHH!"

*She is hit with acid and it seeps into her shoulder wound.  She falls 
backward and stumbles.  The pain is emmence.  She returns fire on Mosquitor. 
  Shooting at him with all her strength.  The pain in growing and she 
wonders how much longer she can hold out.*

"DIE Mosquitor.  YOU HONORLESS PREDACON! DIE!"

*She keeps firing on Mosquitor.  She glimpses over at Striker and Suukie.*

"You guys got anyone for back up? We could use it about now."
